data.description: Spacious three-level townhome situated on large, fenced lot! One of the few in the subdivision with a 2nd full bath! Wood floors! Wall between kitchen and dining area has been removed for a more open feel! Roof is 2 years old! Gas furnace and air conditioning is appr. 10 years old! Hot water heater is 4 years old! New basement door to rear yard! Covered front porch! Large living room! Separate dining room! Kitchen with maple cabinets, double sink, gas cooking, stainless steel side by side refrigerator with custom dispenser! Oversized primary bedroom! Two additional bedrooms with ceiling fans! Full bath on upper level! Basement with large recreation room! Full bath with pocket door in lower level! Separate laundry room on lower level! Walk up steps to backyard! Being sold as-is but has many major updated items! Easy access to Baltimore, Coast Guard, major highways and more! Show and sell!
